{"tid":154257,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父非禮女兒舌舔敏感部位　判囚26個月　官斥視女兒為泄慾工具","createTime":"2017-03-13T07:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T09:01:22.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb88880234d9edcc5e14ddb4440724977b1da0a","tid":154257,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:21:28.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>父非禮女兒舌舔敏感部位　判囚26個月　官斥視女兒為泄慾工具 <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170313/s00001/1489381402407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170313%2Fs00001%2F1489381402407&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruYS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=1e521f34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170313%2Fs00001%2F1489381402407&h=d885acee\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170313/s00001/1489381402407</a></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170313/s00001/1489382927700SL4_057D8CFDC8D9A86F0FC6D4EE0CC937EF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170313%2Fs00001%2F1489382927700SL4_057D8CFDC8D9A86F0FC6D4EE0CC937EF.jpg&h=fe00b172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n退休工人9年前起涉嫌兩度猥褻侵犯當時未成年的女兒，包括舌舔其敏感部位，多年後女兒曾想輕生，最終獲社工協助並揭發事件。法官斥被告當女兒是泄慾工具，判其監禁26個月。<br />\n<br />\n62歲被告育有2子4女，原被控4項猥褻侵犯罪，對象均是其現年19歲的女兒X。被告早前承認2項非禮罪，餘下2項非禮罪則在法庭存檔。<br />\n<br />\n根據案情，2008至2009年某日，當時年僅10至11歲的X因病早退回家，X服藥後躺在牀上，並感到頭暈，其後被告脫去X所有衣物，並親吻她全身，包括胸部及下體；2013年某一天，X在房中小睡片刻，感覺到有人掀起她的校裙，X發現是被告後大叫，被告立即離開。<br />\n<br />\n辯方早前求情時稱，被告犯案是出於疼愛女兒之心，但法官不接納其解釋，指被告把X當成泄慾工具，嚴重違反一名父親照顧女兒的天職；法官又引述X的心理報告指，X入住精神病院宿舍時，竟然有「解脫」的感受，而且當X得知有可能出庭作供時，承受了很大壓力，心理醫生將為X提供進一步的心理輔導。<br />\n<br />\n法官認為判刑須具阻嚇性，決定就兩項非禮罪各判被告入獄2年及4個月，其中2個月刑期分期執行。"},{"pid":"ed62d3faf25d6c5c4b946ae6aa3f64e820af8a3d","tid":154257,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:23:13.000Z","msg":"其實香港好多呢D變態佬 我都想生返個女"},{"pid":"e0a3fecdcf9ca6c064c472ade0907cc209acfc87","tid":154257,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實香港好多呢D變態佬 我都想生返個女</blockquote><br />\n召喚報驚撚"},{"pid":"bd6b293ca881e083a405031b3dad6e0ae3262c96","tid":154257,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實香港好多呢D變態佬 我都想生返個女</blockquote><br />\n召喚報驚撚</blockquote><br />\n報咩警呀你 講事實都唔比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時你見到人地幾兄弟 就知佢老豆想追個女先繼續生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2ec5a41b42da8eef1a5c72c4c13856fa269e94","tid":154257,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:59:54.000Z","msg":"呢d真係拎去斬JJ算啦,唔洗佢坐監"},{"pid":"78cac5ef34be018ecb190e180705f2088dd87afa","tid":154257,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af29f8091c08147dcf032ce1e2d4ec760303c85f","tid":154257,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:13:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37538575c122a719e039299fcfb8e59ef06a19f8","tid":154257,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T08:22:38.000Z","msg":"估錯國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8073abeb31a95947278d08dab71bc548feca93d5","tid":154257,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T09:01:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}